<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="17Apr1931"><font color="red">17 April 1931</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I shall begin my fifth hegira on Sunday (19 April 1931) and hope to arrive in London Whittington-like that evg. (w.p.). Will you please reserve rooms for us at Garland&apos;s (Lucia comes too) </div>
